            <td colspan="2" class="titulo2" valign="top">A Chorus Of Ghosts:  <br><span
 class="texto2">My Argentine Friendship With Ground Zero Videographer<br> Kurt Sonnenfeld <br><br>
 by <a href="../../staff/peter_robertson/bio.php"
 class="link3">Peter Robertson</a><br>
 </span></td>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
            <td><img src="/images/spacer.gif" alt="" border="0"
 height="23" width="1"></td>
